data.description: Take a look at this 3/2 ranch home in the quiet neighborhood of North lauderdale village. This home has been extremely well maintained and cared for by the current owner. Large kitchen with open layout, wood cabinets and granite countertops. Wood flooring throughout living areas, and tile flooring in bedrooms. Large fenced in yard perfect for weekend entertaining! New AC (2018) Roof (2009)
